Colts @ Texans on 10/8 #TNF Sue Baldwin, WUSA 5:36 p.m. EDT October 8, 2015 TNF. 
WASHINGTON (WUSA9) -- #TNF on WUSA9! 
Divisional showdown between Indianapolis and Houston on October 8. 
Game will kick-off at approximately 8:26 p.m. 
Colts are 2-2 and first in the AFC Southern Division. The 1-3 Texans are looking for a win to move up from 3rd place. 
Matt Hasselbeck will start for the injured Andrew Luck. Will he lead Indianapolis to victory or will Houston's defense hold him back? Tune in to find out! 
For coverage leading up to the game, watch WUSA9 News at 5 p.m., 6 p.m. and 7 p.m. 
NFL Thursday Night Kick-off Pre-Game Show airs at 7:30 p.m. 
After the game, WUSA9 News is scheduled at 11:15 p.m. and The Late Show With Stephen Colbert at 11:50 p.m. Times will slide if football overrun.
